experiment_description: Fragments usage and modification probability - In this experiment, the probability of using fragments and the probability of modifiying fragments are changed.

    Blocks
    End
end

3: Blocks = Block

    Block
    Blocks
end
5: Block = while true
    Move
    Bool || break
end

    Move
end
